---
Set or toggle shuffle

Usage: spotuify shuffle [OPTIONS] <STATE>

Arguments:
  <STATE>  Shuffle state [possible values: on, off, toggle]

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format for the mutation receipt [default: table] [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
